nvestment banking division by the summer of  ubs was showing increased signs of stabilization the swiss government sold its chf  billion stake in ubs in late  at a large profit switzerland had purchased convertible notes in  to help ubs clear its balance sheets of toxic assets taking advantage of improved conditions in the stock market in mid ubs placed us billion of shares with a small number of large institutional investors oswald grübel announced we are building a new ubs one that performs to the highest standards and behaves with integrity and honesty one that distinguishes itself not only through the clarity and reliability of the advice and services it provides but in how it manages and executes grübel reiterated plans to maintain an integrated business model of providing wealth management investment banking and asset management services in august  ubs launched a new advertising campaign featuring the slogan we will not rest and signed a global sponsorship agreement with formula  on  october  ubs announced that its private bank recorded net new funds of chf  million during the third quarter compared to an outflow of chf  billion in second quarter ubss third quarter net profit of us billion beat analyst estimates continuing a string of profitability after the elimination of almost  jobs ubs announced on  august  that it was further cutting another  positions in order to improve operating efficiency and save chf  to chf  billion a year  percent of the job cuts would come from the investment banking unit which continued to post dismal figures since the  financial crisis while the rest would come from the wealth management and asset management divisions the firm has seen profits fall due to the rise of the swiss franc on  october  ubs announced that it was cutting  jobs worldwide in an effort to slim down its investment banking operations of which  would be in switzerland followed by the united states and great britain this percent staff cut would make overall sta